b'Doraemon Movie 29: Shin Nobita no Uchu: b"While Nobita is sleeping, he suddenly feels the floor is trembling, like there would be an earthquake in his room. She shows them the passageway through Nobita's floor into the spaceship. After they enter the spaceship, they see the Koya Koya Planet. they meet a boy named Roppuru..."
